<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>2026 Queen's Bughouse Championship - Queen's Chess Club</title>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Vollkorn:ital,wght@0,400..900;1,400..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=League+Spartan:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.1/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="images/logo.jpg"/>

    <style>
        .bughouse-page {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #120c09 0%, #21140d 36%, #f8f1e7 36%, #f8f1e7 100%);
            padding-bottom: 70px;
        }

        .bughouse-shell {
            width: min(1160px, calc(100% - 32px));
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .bughouse-hero {
            padding: 70px 0 46px;
            color: white;
        }

        .bughouse-hero__eyebrow {
            display: inline-block;
            font-family: 'League Spartan', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #ffcf6b;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .bughouse-hero__content {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.4fr) minmax(300px, 0.9fr);
            gap: 28px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .bughouse-hero h1 {
            font-family: 'League Spartan', sans-serif;
            font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 4.9rem);
            line-height: 0.95;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin: 0 0 18px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            max-width: 760px;
            color: #d4af37;
        }

        .bughouse-hero p {
            font-family: 'Vollkorn', serif;
            font-size: 1.16rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #f1dfcc;
            margin: 0 0 26px;
            max-width: 640px;
        }

        .bughouse-tag-row {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .bughouse-tag {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 207, 107, 0.28);
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            font-family: 'League Spartan', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.92rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            color: white;
        }

        .bughouse-side-card {
            background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(255, 204, 103, 0.16), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05));
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 26px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
            box-shadow: 0 22px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
        }

        .bughouse-side-card h2 {
            margin: 0 0 14px;
            font-family: 'League Spartan', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            color: #ffcf6b;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .bughouse-side-card ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            color: #f6eadf;
            font-family: 'Vollkorn', serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-size: 1.02rem;
        }

        .bughouse-main {
            margin-top: 18px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.3fr) minmax(310px, 0.9fr);
            gap: 28px;
            align-items: start;
        }

        .bughouse-panel {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 45px rgba(20, 12, 9, 0.08);
            padding: 34px;
        }

        .bughouse-highlight {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c1d16 0%, #4a2a18 100%);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 22px;
            padding: 26px 28px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .bughouse-highlight h2 {
            margin: 0 0 12px;
            font-family: 'League Spartan', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.65rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.8px;
            color: #ffcf6b;
        }

        .bughouse-highlight p,
        .bughouse-panel p,
        .bughouse-panel li,
        .register-card p,
        .register-card li {
            font-family: 'Vollkorn', serif;
            font-size: 1.04rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #443028;
        }

        .bughouse-highlight p {
            color: #f3e7dd;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .bughouse-section + .bughouse-section {
            margin-top: 28px;
        }

        .bughouse-section h3 {
            margin: 0 0 14px;
            font-family: 'League Spartan', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.45rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.7px;
            color: #251712;
        }

        .bughouse-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 18px;
            margin-top: 18px;
        }

        .bughouse-info-card,
        .register-card,
        .prize-card {
            background: #fffaf4;
            border: 1px solid #efd9c4;
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 22px;
        }

        .bughouse-info-card h4,
        .register-card h3,
        .prize-card h4 {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            font-family: 'League Spartan', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.08rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.7px;
            color: #9f4529;
        }

        .bughouse-info-card p,
        .prize-card p {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .prize-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 18px;
            margin-top: 18px;
        }

        .prize-card {
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff7ec 0%, #fff 100%);
        }

        .prize-card .place {
            display: block;
            font-family: 'League Spartan', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.92rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #8d7768;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .prize-card .amount {
            display: block;
            font-family: 'League Spartan', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1;
            color: #cf5f23;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .register-card {
            position: sticky;
            top: 24px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff9f2 0%, #ffffff 100%);
        }

        .register-button {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: #cf5f23;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: 'League Spartan', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
            margin: 14px 0 18px;
        }

        .register-button:hover {
            color: white;
            background: #b94f16;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .register-link {
            word-break: break-word;
            color: #9f4529;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .register-list {
            margin: 0 0 20px;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .qr-wrapper {
            margin-top: 18px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .qr-wrapper img {
            width: min(240px, 100%);
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 18px;
            border: 8px solid white;
            box-shadow: 0 14px 34px rgba(25, 12, 7, 0.12);
            background: white;
        }

        .qr-caption {
            margin-top: 12px;
            font-family: 'Vollkorn', serif;
            font-size: 0.98rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #5e4337;
        }

        .contact-strip {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 18px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ecd9c8;
        }

        .contact-strip a {
            color: #9f4529;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .contact-strip a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        @media (max-width: 940px) {
            .bughouse-hero__content,
            .bughouse-main,
            .bughouse-grid,
            .prize-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .register-card {
                position: static;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .bughouse-page {
                background: linear-gradient(180deg, #120c09 0%, #24150d 27%, #f8f1e7 27%, #f8f1e7 100%);
            }

            .bughouse-hero {
                padding-top: 52px;
            }

            .bughouse-panel,
            .register-card,
            .bughouse-highlight {
                padding: 24px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<%- include('header.ejs') %>

<body>
    <div class="bughouse-page">
        <div class="bughouse-shell">
            <section class="bughouse-hero">
                <div class="bughouse-hero__content">
                    <div>
                        <div class="bughouse-hero__eyebrow">Queen's Chess Club presents</div>
                        <h1>2026 Queen's Bughouse Championship</h1>
                        <p>Bughouse is taking over the old QCC slot this year. Grab a partner for a fast, team-based event with round robin pairings, a 5+0 time control, and cash prizes for the top two teams.</p>
                        <div class="bughouse-tag-row">
                            <span class="bughouse-tag">March 28, 2026</span>
                            <span class="bughouse-tag">2:00 PM</span>
                            <span class="bughouse-tag">Kingston Hall 208</span>
                            <span class="bughouse-tag">Teams of 2</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <aside class="bughouse-side-card">
                        <h2>Quick Snapshot</h2>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Format: Round robin</li>
                            <li>Time control: 5+0</li>
                            <li>Entry fee: $10 for all players</li>
                            <li>Prizes: $50 for first, $40 for second</li>
                            <li>Need a partner? Individuals can also be paired on-site</li>
                        </ul>
                    </aside>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="bughouse-main">
                <div class="bughouse-panel">
                    <div class="bughouse-highlight">
                        <h2>Register Online or On-Site</h2>
                        <p>Use the Google Form ahead of time to reserve your spot, or sign up in person on the day of the event. Teams may register together, and players without a partner can still attend and be paired on-site.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bughouse-section">
                        <h3>Event Details</h3>
                        <p>The 2026 Queen's Bughouse Championship is a team event built around speed, coordination, and chaos in the best possible way. Each team has two players, and pieces captured by one teammate can be dropped by the other.</p>
                        <div class="bughouse-grid">
                            <div class="bughouse-info-card">
                                <h4>When</h4>
                                <p>Saturday, March 28th, 2026<br>Games begin at 2:00 PM</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bughouse-info-card">
                                <h4>Where</h4>
                                <p>Kingston Hall 208<br>Queen's University</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bughouse-info-card">
                                <h4>Format</h4>
                                <p>Round robin teams event<br>5+0 time control</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bughouse-info-card">
                                <h4>Who Can Play</h4>
                                <p>Open entry with no rating limits<br>Students and non-students welcome</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bughouse-section">
                        <h3>Prizes and Entry</h3>
                        <p>The event costs $10 per player. Monetary prizes are awarded by team standing and will be divided between teammates.</p>
                        <div class="prize-grid">
                            <div class="prize-card">
                                <span class="place">First Place</span>
                                <span class="amount">$50</span>
                                <p>Top finishing team</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="prize-card">
                                <span class="place">Second Place</span>
                                <span class="amount">$40</span>
                                <p>Runner-up team</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bughouse-section">
                        <h3>Registration Notes</h3>
                        <p>If you already have a teammate, include their name in the form. If not, you can still register solo or simply come to the event and we will help pair individuals on-site. Entry fees can be paid by e-transfer to <strong>queenschess@outlook.com</strong> or with exact cash on-site.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <aside class="register-card">
                    <h3>Sign Up</h3>
                    <p>Register here for the 2026 Queen's Bughouse Championship:</p>
                    <a class="register-button" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeYxOY91dxeh_GFkRjNIr-imMualomGKCkCe9v2xQjO2qAnTw/viewform" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                        <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
                        Open Google Form
                    </a>

                    <ul class="register-list">
                        <li>Add your teammate if you already have one.</li>
                        <li>If you do not have a partner, you can still register and be paired on-site.</li>
                        <li>Choose e-transfer or cash on-site when submitting the form.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <div class="qr-wrapper">
                        <img src="https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=240x240&data=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeYxOY91dxeh_GFkRjNIr-imMualomGKCkCe9v2xQjO2qAnTw%2Fviewform" alt="QR code linking to the 2026 Queen's Bughouse Championship Google Form">
                        <p class="qr-caption">Scan this QR code to open the registration form directly on your phone.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="contact-strip">
                        <p>Questions or concerns? Email <a href="mailto:queenschess@outlook.com">queenschess@outlook.com</a>.</p>
                    </div>
                </aside>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('footer.ejs'); %>
</body>
</html>
